reviews.text: Second time at this place.  Love the chili sichuan fish... it's grilled and then comes in a shallow pot that is heated over one of the portable stoves.  Very flavourful!

A famous fish shop with 8 cooking styles for fishes . Fishes are good comparing with the other shops . Besides , they offer Sichuan Skewers and Guang Dong dishes . This is a place for you to spend Lunch , Dinner or Late night gatherings .

You can choose spicy levels for skewers / fishes

Came here on Friday evening, place was about half full. Ordered fish in the fermented vegetables sour soup. Fish tasted fresh and was very tender, soup was a bit salty but still tasty. Also got some satay, it was ok, not exceptional. Service was friendly and fairly fast.
I like local restaurant. Some restaurants service level is bad but here is nice, I could spend good time to eat delicious seafood. Fish hot pot price is HKD200-300 depend on kind/ size of fish.
Famous spicy fish dish. delicious. mush try.

얼큰한 마라생선찜!
메뉴판에서 맨 윗줄 오른쪽 사천식 생선찜을 추천해주시길래 시켰다. 느끼한 요리에 질릴 때 쯤 매운뽕을 채워주는 메뉴다

우리만 외국인이여서 신기하셨나보다 겁나 맛있게 먹구있는데 점원분들 다 뿌듯하게 쳐다보셨음..
